  "detailed_description": "<strong>Keep it casual with this single-player offline mini golf game.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408710/extras/2139c70cdfe536dcaf225ae0e4b476d9.poster.avif?t=1773428947\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408710/extras/2139c70cdfe536dcaf225ae0e4b476d9.webm?t=1773428947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408710/extras/2139c70cdfe536dcaf225ae0e4b476d9.mp4?t=1773428947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are 18 holes of Small Golf & 18 holes of Mini Golf!<br><br>In Small Golf, which is golf on a small scale, you play with 3 clubs, a pitching wedge, a sand wedge, and a putter. <br><br>Both Small Golf & Classic Mini Golf have 2 game modes, normal play & par or under.<br>In the normal play game mode, you need to sink your ball to move on to the next hole, regardless of your score, no surprises there.<br>In the par or under game mode, you must sink your ball within par to move on to the next hole. <br><br><strong>Par or under is much more challenging but both are great fun to play.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Keep it casual with this single-player offline mini golf game.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408710/extras/2139c70cdfe536dcaf225ae0e4b476d9.poster.avif?t=1773428947\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408710/extras/2139c70cdfe536dcaf225ae0e4b476d9.webm?t=1773428947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408710/extras/2139c70cdfe536dcaf225ae0e4b476d9.mp4?t=1773428947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are 18 holes of Small Golf & 18 holes of Mini Golf!<br><br>In Small Golf, which is golf on a small scale, you play with 3 clubs, a pitching wedge, a sand wedge, and a putter. <br><br>Both Small Golf & Classic Mini Golf have 2 game modes, normal play & par or under.<br>In the normal play game mode, you need to sink your ball to move on to the next hole, regardless of your score, no surprises there.<br>In the par or under game mode, you must sink your ball within par to move on to the next hole. <br><br><strong>Par or under is much more challenging but both are great fun to play.</strong>",
